{"tid":1746634,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[11.23 0700] 隻「禿鷹」曾偉雄 落－選－了！","createTime":"2019-11-22T23:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T04:04:02.000Z","uid":282569,"like":388,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"a63f59412b2e7f4d3e94083b35ed2969881eca10","tid":1746634,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T23:08:58.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉FB - 堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glos World is with Simon Shen<br />\n<br />\n【#突發超大喜訊 🇪🇬🇭🇰 】聯合國手足傳來特大喜訊：前香港警務署署長「禿鷹」曾偉雄，獲中國政府高調全力支持，競逐聯合國維也納辦事處(UNOV)總幹事、暨聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室(UNODC)行政總監一職，雖然曾被視為熱門，並進入最後一輪面試，但正式宣佈失敗！<br />\n<br />\n經過fact-checked，果然聯合國剛宣佈任命埃及社會團結部長Ghada Fathi Waly，擔任這兩大職務。月前呼籲各位手足去信、聯署聯合國，反對禿鷹掌管這全球掃毒第一要職，努力並沒有白費。這是中國外交近年的重大挫敗，也是國際社會對香港警察近來行為的最好表態。<br />\n<br />\n#唔係天方夜譚 #你無揀錯<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：聯合國維也納辦事處任命曾偉雄為總幹事？<br />\n<a href=\"https://simonshen.blog/2019/07/22/聯合國維也納辦事處-任命曾偉雄-為總幹事？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsimonshen.blog%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%AD%E4%B9%9F%E7%B4%8D%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95-%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84-%E7%82%BA%E7%B8%BD%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=17c4967c\" target=\"_blank\">https://simonshen.blog/2019/07/22/聯合國維也納辦事處-任命曾偉雄-為總幹事？/</a><br />\n<br />\nEgyptian minister Ghada Waly picked to head UN drug agency<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/egyptian-minister-ghada-waly-picked-to-head-un-drug-agency-1.941263?fbclid=IwAR1jztJzJNFUpq65TrNO4NjcW3qTnRsicAgl990jzsoVQZZ9FL8CnCF-BPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenational.ae%2Fworld%2Fmena%2Fegyptian-minister-ghada-waly-picked-to-head-un-drug-agency-1.941263%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1jztJzJNFUpq65TrNO4NjcW3qTnRsicAgl990jzsoVQZZ9FL8CnCF-BPI&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=dc8baa7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/egyptian-minister-ghada-waly-picked-to-head-un-drug-agency-1.941263?fbclid=IwAR1jztJ